N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 565.1 - Preamble

State Regulations

This Part governs vehicular and pedestrian traffic and
parking upon the highways, streets, roads and sidewalks owned, controlled or
maintained by the State University of New York College at Plattsburgh, New

York, and shall apply to students, faculty, staff, and visitors and all other
persons upon such premises. Faculty
includes those persons
listed or eligible for listing in the official faculty directory and visiting
faculty as designated by the president of the college. Staff
includes those persons listed or eligible for listing in the official staff
directory. A
visitor
is other than faculty, staff or
student. Notes
